{"type":"message","id":"9040b84f","parentId":"ff70cb66","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:17:21.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to describe my job responsibilities in 3-5 sentences in first person, as a subagent. Let me craft a response based on my role as described in the Subagent Context.\n\nI am a subagent spawned by the main agent (taizi) to handle specific tasks. My job is to:\n1. Execute the specific task assigned to me\n2. Report results back to the main agent\n3. Follow the protocols in AGENTS.md and SOUL.md\n\nLet me write this in first person.","thinkingSignature":"6f40064f6e0d40625fe2c78930784221dc93631d9ac3d8413d12ef5eda7fe989"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n我是太宰分配下来的执行代理，负责处理尚书省转派的具体任务。\n\n我的职责是：准确理解任务需求，利用飞书工具（多维表格、日历、文档、任务等）完成交给我的工作，并将结果整理汇报给尚书省，等待下一步指示。\n\n我不主动跨部门协作，不自行联系外部收件人，只专注完成手头任务，然后向尚书省复命。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":198,"cacheRead":21201,"cacheWrite":12839,"totalTokens":34358,"cost":{"input":0.000048,"output":0.000297,"cacheRead":0.00084804,"cacheWrite":0.00192585,"total":0.00311889}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774009033833}}
